---
import TerminalPanel from '../../components/TerminalPanel.astro';
import { services } from '../../data/services';
import { soundCloudProfile } from '../../data/tracks';
import SiteLayout from '../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
const discordProfileUrl = 'https://discord.com/users/576348645742608387';
---

<SiteLayout
  title="Commissions"
  description="Music production commissions for custom beats, mixing, beat licences and full song production."
>
  <div class="site-stack commissions-stack">
    <h1 class="sr-only">Commissions</h1>

    <section aria-labelledby="pricing-title">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <h2 id="pricing-title">Choose a service</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="pricing-intro">Pick what’s closest to what you need, then send me the details and I’ll confirm the final price before I start. Starting prices are in AUD.</p>

      <div class="pricing-grid">
        {services.map((service) => (
          <article class="price-card" box-="square">
            <h3>{service.name}</h3>
            <p class="price"><small>from</small> {service.price}</p>
            <p class="summary">{service.summary}</p>
            <ul>
              {service.includes.map((item) => <li>{item}</li>)}
            </ul>
            <a href="#contact">Ask about this service <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>

    </section>

    <section aria-labelledby="workflow-title">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <h2 id="workflow-title">How commissions work</h2>
      </div>
      <ol class="flow-list">
        <li><strong>01 / Send</strong><p>Use the contact details below to send me a short project brief.</p></li>
        <li><strong>02 / Quote</strong><p>Scope, price, revisions, rights and timing are confirmed in writing.</p></li>
        <li><strong>03 / Create</strong><p>A first pass is produced and shared at the agreed review point.</p></li>
        <li><strong>04 / Finish</strong><p>Feedback is applied and the approved files are delivered.</p></li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <TerminalPanel id="contact" class="contact-panel" shear="none">
      <div class="contact-grid">
        <div class="contact-copy">
          <h2>Contact</h2>
          <p>Discord is the best way to reach me. You can also use my SoundCloud profile.</p>

          <div class="contact-list">
            <div class="contact-row">
              <span>Discord</span>
              <strong>helpimdead111</strong>
              <a href={discordProfileUrl} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Open ↗</a>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-row">
              <span>SoundCloud</span>
              <strong>@kashii</strong>
              <a href={soundCloudProfile} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Open ↗</a>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

        <div class="message-template">
          <div class="template-heading">
            <h3>Include useful details</h3>
            <button type="button" id="copy-template">Copy template</button>
          </div>
          <div class="template-columns">
            <div>
              <h4>Template</h4>
              <pre id="message-template">Hi, I’m [your name].

Service: [e.g. custom beat]
Project: [what you want made]
Reference links: [two or three songs with a similar sound]
Budget: [your budget in AUD]
Deadline: [the date you need it by]
Intended use: [e.g. Spotify release, YouTube video or personal use]

Anything else I should know: [vocals, stems or other useful details]</pre>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4>Example</h4>
              <pre>Hi, I’m Alex.

Service: Custom beat
Project: A fast electronic track for a vocal single
Reference links: Two SoundCloud or Spotify track URLs
Budget: $180
Deadline: 20 September 2026
Intended use: Spotify and YouTube release

Anything else I should know: I have the vocals recorded and would also like an instrumental version.</pre>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p id="contact-status" role="status" aria-live="polite"></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </TerminalPanel>

    <section aria-labelledby="faq-title">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <h2 id="faq-title">Q&A</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-grid">
        <article class="faq-card">
          <h3>What should I send?</h3>
          <p>A short goal, two or three references, your budget, deadline and anything already recorded. Voice memos and rough demos are useful.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="faq-card">
          <h3>Are the listed prices final?</h3>
          <p>They are starting prices in AUD. The final quote reflects scope, turnaround and intended usage, and is confirmed before work starts.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="faq-card">
          <h3>Who owns the finished music?</h3>
          <p>Usage rights vary by service. The agreed licence, credits and permitted use will be written into the quote before production begins.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="faq-card">
          <h3>How long will it take?</h3>
          <p>Timing depends on the project and my current queue. Include your deadline so I can confirm availability up front.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="faq-card">
          <h3>How does payment work?</h3>
          <p>Payments are arranged through a parent or guardian. Half is due before work starts, and the other half is due after final approval but before the finished files are delivered. Prices and invoices are in AUD; international clients may be charged a conversion fee by their payment provider.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="faq-card">
          <h3>What is the refund policy?</h3>
          <p>If I can’t complete the agreed project, the up-front payment will be refunded. If you cancel after work starts, the up-front payment is not refundable because it covers work already completed.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <script src="../../scripts/contact.ts"></script>
</SiteLayout>

<style>
  .commissions-stack {
    gap: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 5.5rem);
  }

  .pricing-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .pricing-intro {
    margin-block: 0 1.25rem;
    color: var(--foreground1);
  }

  .price-card {
    min-width: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    border-color: var(--panel-border);
    background: var(--panel-bg);
    padding: clamp(1.1rem, 3vw, 1.6rem);
    box-shadow: var(--panel-shadow);
  }

  .price-card h3 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 3vw, 1.8rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  }

  .price {
    margin-block: 0.5rem 0;
    color: var(--accent-soft);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.4rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.07em;
  }

  .price small {
    color: var(--foreground2);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  .summary {
    margin-block: 0.9rem 0;
    color: var(--foreground1);
  }

  .price-card ul {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.45rem;
    margin-block: 1rem 1.3rem;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
    color: var(--foreground1);
    font-size: 0.86rem;
  }

  .price-card li::before {
    content: '+ ';
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .price-card > a {
    margin-block-start: auto;
    color: var(--accent-soft);
    font-weight: 700;
  }


  .contact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.75fr) minmax(0, 1.25fr);
    gap: clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
  }

  .contact-copy h2 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.055em;
  }

  .contact-copy > p {
    margin-block: 0.9rem 1.4rem;
    color: var(--foreground1);
  }

  .contact-list {
    margin-block-end: 1.25rem;
    border-block-end: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--foreground2) 30%, transparent);
  }

  .contact-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 6.5rem minmax(0, 1fr) auto;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding-block: 0.85rem;
    border-block-start: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--foreground2) 30%, transparent);
  }

  .contact-row > span {
    color: var(--foreground2);
    font-size: 0.76rem;
  }

  .contact-row strong {
    min-width: 0;
    overflow-wrap: anywhere;
  }

  .contact-row a,
  #copy-template {
    border: 0;
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--accent-soft);
    padding: 0;
    font: inherit;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 0.2em;
  }

  .message-template {
    min-width: 0;
    border: 1px solid var(--control-border);
    background: var(--background0);
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  .template-heading {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .template-heading h3 {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .template-columns {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .template-columns > div {
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .template-columns h4 {
    margin-block: 1rem 0.5rem;
    color: var(--foreground1);
  }

  .message-template pre {
    height: calc(100% - 2rem);
    margin: 0;
    padding: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--foreground2) 28%, transparent);
    background: var(--background1);
    color: var(--foreground1);
    font: inherit;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    white-space: pre-wrap;
  }

  #contact-status {
    min-height: 1.25rem;
    margin-block: 0.65rem 0;
    color: var(--accent-green);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
  }

  .faq-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1px;
    padding: 1px;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--foreground2) 28%, transparent);
  }

  .faq-card {
    background: var(--background1);
    padding: 1.1rem;
  }

  .faq-card h3 {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--foreground0);
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .faq-card p {
    margin-block: 0.8rem 0;
    color: var(--foreground1);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .pricing-grid,
    .contact-grid,
    .template-columns,
    .faq-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .contact-row {
      grid-template-columns: 5.5rem minmax(0, 1fr) auto;
    }
  }
</style>
